{"tid":1630724,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"RTHK 記者被燃燒物擊中，割定唔割？","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T02:47:56.000Z","uid":262664,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5d364eb679ed4764c84ee60b566f5cb9cbad847c","tid":1630724,"uid":262664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:28:29.000Z","msg":"當事人都唔割，成班膠就爭住割 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁中意割去割自己包皮啦<br />\n根本連回應都唔需要<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7kybcXC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7kybcXC.jpg&h=978c32de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aab284640216a875d3e617e3dd663a47905fb44f","tid":1630724,"uid":6310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"真, 成班係到屌屌屌, 屌你老母學撚下對家藍尸廢老黑警啦, 真係核爆都唔撚割呀<br />\n屌你宜家係到捉自己人, 食屎狗"},{"pid":"93851f8dfa2fa6e9c162f6c7199e0c412b85b121","tid":1630724,"uid":22772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:19:24.000Z","msg":"唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34be62253c39234cf1c60f2a19c924e4b7b48289","tid":1630724,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:19:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"ae7d4dedd2ee8617f5f77443668367ab19dec74f","tid":1630724,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:20:21.000Z","msg":"記者保護市民<br />\n係香港市民嘅天使<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df45d4f68522d2d417571535cbedf2dbdb510a44","tid":1630724,"uid":121246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"感謝港台，香港人嘅電台<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力 <br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰"},{"pid":"a57456badf584da97b6eefa9c2162afc48fa570e","tid":1630724,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:43:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84b3ac056552e7f32dc6510b19a4ec00b0f8ac9d","tid":1630724,"uid":211364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:48:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"99dd6362fa53658fdc8326170960ab29717e68b4","tid":1630724,"uid":22707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"對唔住<br />\n辛苦哂<br />\n<br />\n多謝你地 rthk ❤️"},{"pid":"b1f50f3949e5d2bb920bf993ed95061c9694def0","tid":1630724,"uid":168250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:53:19.000Z","msg":"道聲歉，對唔住記者，唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔完美，絕對需要改善"},{"pid":"869eb44a5bb6887e1dc450037e0b5783c61a5163","tid":1630724,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:53:52.000Z","msg":"Say個sor點都要，始終燒到自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但好似樓主咁講<br />\n當事人都未割你哋割乜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4660b3cb7da1f7d96020548f05c5fd24b60b2e9d","tid":1630724,"uid":136735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:57:08.000Z","msg":"屌屌屌割割割果班人屌哂你地老母閪<br />\n你有本錢割咩屌你老母"},{"pid":"8c85d85bfbb4d7d3b4a84dc629e361ba90d6bff0","tid":1630724,"uid":206370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:00:34.000Z","msg":"割你老母咩"},{"pid":"503ec81144baf3abcfbf31bf293068fc7d923f95","tid":1630724,"uid":82588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:01:06.000Z","msg":"不分化不割蓆不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n罵不還手 只還口<br />\n打不還口 要還手<br />\n<br />\n良心黃店要懲罰<br />\n中資藍店要罷買<br />\n仆街黑店要裝修"},{"pid":"8b7ebae52a7d5078fb7f8a7d73c1e48e5f4aacaa","tid":1630724,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:02:16.000Z","msg":"要道歉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>一個準則可以破到而家死局</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"842fe22579bfb52d54f115f67335244c2c044c16","tid":1630724,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:03:15.000Z","msg":"唔割<br />\n但係一定要道歉<br />\n唔係自己人就大撚哂架，好彩就話無事姐"},{"pid":"a4eaad0079b0885da193c7b25d35834854c88b08","tid":1630724,"uid":62610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:05:20.000Z","msg":"表示深切慰問, 希望早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b606f8ee39090fafe4d883c4b3c0feecf61345e","tid":1630724,"uid":224929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:11:35.000Z","msg":"人地都講左不割囉，仲諗割唔割蓆？<br />\n不過，手足下次出魔法要小心d留意下隊友同記者！ 不完美，可改善！希望記者朋友可以早日康復！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce687bee005179e38dc7b56c3a63c9746ef917c","tid":1630724,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"有無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}